"  Cupcakes:","2 cups all-purpose flour","1 teaspoon baking powder","3/4 teaspoon baking soda","  Pinch of salt","8 tablespoons (1 stick) unsalted butter, at room temperature","1 1/2 cups packed light brown sugar","2  large eggs","1 cup mashed ripe bananas (about 2 large bananas)","1/4 cup plain yogurt","1 teaspoon vanilla extract","  Frosting:","4 ounces chocolate chips","6 tablespoons unsalted butter, at room temperature","1 1/2 cups confectioners' sugar, sifted","1 tablespoon whole milk","1 teaspoon vanilla extract"